title: Immigrant Orphans Adopted by U.S. Citizens by Gender, Age, and Region and Country of Birth, Fiscal Year 2008
name: Immigrant Orphans Adopted by U.S. Citizens by Gender, Age, and Region and Country of Birth, Fiscal Year 2008
description:
This dataset displays data on Immigrant Orphans Adopted by US Citizens by Gender, Age, Region, and Country during 2008.

The data comes from DHS and includes: country, total, male, female, age under one, age 1 to 4, age 5 and over.

To note: Korea, Republic of contains data for both North and South Korea.

If a country has a field of "D" the data is defined as data withheld to limit disclosure.
